1
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:40,150
[Born to Be Alive]

2
00:01:40,170 --> 00:01:43,229
[Episode 29]

3
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:44,570
Didn't you say

4
00:01:44,590 --> 00:01:46,520
you'd finish the search last year?

5
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:52,820
I'm just afraid that
if I finish searching this year...

6
00:01:53,690 --> 00:01:54,590
I won't know

7
00:01:54,620 --> 00:01:56,420
what to do with myself next year.

8
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:03,640
Five stages of grief.

9
00:02:10,139 --> 00:02:12,510
When people experience grief,

10
00:02:12,990 --> 00:02:14,590
they go through five stages.

11
00:02:16,650 --> 00:02:17,460
Denial,

12
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,180
anger,

13
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,180
bargaining,

14
00:02:22,810 --> 00:02:23,470
de...

15
00:02:25,020 --> 00:02:25,620
De...

16
00:02:25,730 --> 00:02:26,670
Depression.

17
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,720
Acceptance.

18
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:31,320
First comes

19
00:02:32,110 --> 00:02:32,860
denial.

20
00:02:33,579 --> 00:02:34,590
Then anger.

21
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:37,500
Then bargaining begins.

22
00:02:38,060 --> 00:02:38,840
Then

23
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:41,020
comes depression.

24
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,329
Finally, with no choice,

25
00:02:42,329 --> 00:02:43,400
you accept it.

26
00:02:44,850 --> 00:02:46,130
Of course, some people

27
00:02:46,460 --> 00:02:47,800
will cycle between

28
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:49,000
certain stages.

29
00:02:49,370 --> 00:02:49,710
And, of course,

30
00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:51,370
there are also people like Han

31
00:02:51,630 --> 00:02:53,210
who get stuck in a certain stage

32
00:02:53,210 --> 00:02:54,190
and need a long time

33
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,200
to move on.

34
00:02:58,190 --> 00:02:59,150
Han,

35
00:03:00,020 --> 00:03:00,870
Bai Ji said

36
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:02,460
this is aged baijiu.

37
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:03,640
You're wasting it by drinking like that...

38
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:04,030
People like you,

39
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:05,890
who've already gone through
all five stages,

40
00:03:05,890 --> 00:03:07,150
wouldn't understand!

41
00:03:09,310 --> 00:03:10,080
Bai,

42
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:12,930
actually...

43
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:17,060
you haven't gone through
all the stages either.

44
00:03:17,690 --> 00:03:18,500
I know.

45
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,550
Cheers.

46
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:26,160
Seriously, this won't work,

47
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,310
that won't work—

48
00:03:27,410 --> 00:03:28,410
only booze works.

49
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,370
Drink up. Drink.

50
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,120
Good liquor or bad liquor...

51
00:03:35,500 --> 00:03:37,500
I really can't tell the difference.

52
00:03:39,090 --> 00:03:41,620
Dongzhiba always said
alcohol tasted awful.

53
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,180
So every time I drink a new one,

54
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,600
I want him to try it too...

55
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:55,160
and ask him if it's any good.

56
00:03:56,829 --> 00:03:59,160
And... and He.

57
00:04:00,530 --> 00:04:02,000
The gunman who killed him

58
00:04:02,020 --> 00:04:03,870
still hasn't been caught.

59
00:04:05,860 --> 00:04:07,150
I thought

60
00:04:08,510 --> 00:04:10,840
once the Forestry Police was established

61
00:04:11,650 --> 00:04:13,850
and the Mountain Patrol was disbanded,

62
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,690
I'd be the first to go.

63
00:04:21,190 --> 00:04:22,420
Now the Captain

64
00:04:23,100 --> 00:04:24,360
and the Deputy Captain

65
00:04:25,670 --> 00:04:26,650
are both gone.

66
00:04:37,710 --> 00:04:38,620
Bai.

67
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:41,880
I just caused a scene

68
00:04:41,909 --> 00:04:42,840
at the coal mine,

69
00:04:44,130 --> 00:04:45,190
and you arrested me

70
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,500
like I was your enemy.

71
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,130
Tell me,

72
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,820
are you still my friend or not?

73
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:58,840
Wipe it off yourself with your clothes.

74
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,880
Where are you wiping?

75
00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:04,020
You drunk or what?

76
00:05:04,860 --> 00:05:05,340
Come here. Come on.

77
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,470
I'll wipe it for you.

78
00:05:09,660 --> 00:05:10,590
Shao,

79
00:05:10,990 --> 00:05:12,250
you're a piece of work.

80
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:16,000
It's so hard for Bai Ju
to raise the child alone.

81
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,380
What kind of father

82
00:05:17,380 --> 00:05:18,550
are you?

83
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:23,100
If we'd known you two wouldn't work out,

84
00:05:23,100 --> 00:05:23,630
why did we all

85
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:24,770
bother setting you up?

86
00:05:24,770 --> 00:05:25,540
Alright.

87
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,630
Here's the thing.

88
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,190
I'm...

89
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:34,760
getting a promotion soon.

90
00:05:35,130 --> 00:05:36,250
After that, I'll

91
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,420
spend more time

92
00:05:37,420 --> 00:05:38,450
with the kid.

93
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,159
Next year, I'll take Zhuling

94
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,610
to the provincial capital for school.

95
00:05:41,610 --> 00:05:42,700
Bai Ju will go too.

96
00:05:43,600 --> 00:05:44,420
Really?

97
00:05:45,290 --> 00:05:46,830
That depends on his behavior.

98
00:05:46,830 --> 00:05:48,230
You're all my witnesses.

99
00:05:48,659 --> 00:05:50,060
Help me keep an eye on him.

100
00:05:51,170 --> 00:05:51,870
Heard that?

101
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:56,620
Good.

102
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,230
Good.

103
00:06:01,250 --> 00:06:02,630
You guys just move on.

104
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:06,280
With us here,

105
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,440
we'll hold the fort.

106
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,660
Just move on!

107
00:06:10,570 --> 00:06:11,980
Go without worry!

108
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:14,720
Crying again?

109
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,210
Han, give it a rest.

110
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:18,420
And you.

111
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,400
Look at you!

112
00:06:20,570 --> 00:06:21,690
What's wrong with me?

113
00:06:21,690 --> 00:06:22,680
You know what's wrong with you!

114
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,450
I'm just minding my own business,

115
00:06:23,450 --> 00:06:24,480
running my supermarket.

116
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,430
If we're talking about
environmental protection,

117
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:26,560
I'm the most eco-friendly one here.

118
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,060
I even volunteer for it.

119
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:33,120
You're the worst friend!

120
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:34,950
You won't even drink with us!

121
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:35,900
Drink  it.

122
00:06:35,930 --> 00:06:37,180
Han, Han!

123
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:37,860
Han!

124
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:38,810
Ever since Sangba

125
00:06:38,810 --> 00:06:40,270
had heart surgery,

126
00:06:40,830 --> 00:06:42,540
his wife hasn't let him drink.

127
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:44,050
He has to be careful.

128
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:46,010
I think you're the worst friend.

129
00:06:46,030 --> 00:06:47,100
Shut up, you!

130
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:48,690
You're the one who benefits the most!

131
00:06:48,690 --> 00:06:49,720
What did I do?

132
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:50,600
What did you do?

133
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,190
You've got money.

134
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:53,830
You're the richest one here.

135
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:54,720
Big shot.

136
00:06:54,810 --> 00:06:56,370
Driving that big truck!

137
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,659
Alright, alright!

138
00:06:57,990 --> 00:06:59,320
Then come herd the yaks for me,

139
00:06:59,320 --> 00:06:59,820
okay?

140
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:01,540
I'm not going to work for you!

141
00:07:03,810 --> 00:07:05,170
I won't work for anyone!

142
00:07:06,010 --> 00:07:07,370
I'm just a loser.

143
00:07:07,940 --> 00:07:09,250
I can't do anything.

144
00:07:10,270 --> 00:07:11,800
All I've got is a foul mouth.

145
00:07:16,010 --> 00:07:18,070
I'll rip this foul mouth of mine off!

146
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,510
Alright, alright!

147
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:21,160
I'll help you rip it off.

148
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,780
You can't do it yourself.

149
00:07:23,330 --> 00:07:24,410
I'll help you.

150
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:27,920
I'll rip yours first!

151
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,090
They're fighting.

152
00:07:29,230 --> 00:07:29,660
Rip it!

153
00:07:29,690 --> 00:07:30,420
What a fight!

154
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,300
Rip!

155
00:07:31,330 --> 00:07:32,390
Look at this fight.

156
00:07:56,930 --> 00:07:58,420
This is reporter Shao Yunfei,

157
00:07:58,420 --> 00:08:00,160
reporting live from the scene.

158
00:08:29,270 --> 00:08:30,070
She's asleep?

159
00:08:31,110 --> 00:08:31,690
Yeah.

160
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,700
Well, I'll be off then.

161
00:08:39,289 --> 00:08:39,890
Tomorrow at 8 AM,

162
00:08:39,890 --> 00:08:41,090
I'll come pick you up.

163
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,409
Take that suitcase

164
00:08:43,409 --> 00:08:44,480
to the car first.

165
00:08:44,650 --> 00:08:45,120
Okay.

166
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,170
It's been a long time

167
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:55,650
since I tucked her in

168
00:08:55,650 --> 00:08:56,820
like this.

169
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:58,220
I thought...

170
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:03,460
Thank you.

171
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,360
See you tomorrow.

172
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,840
See you tomorrow.

173
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:31,630
Chun.

174
00:09:33,110 --> 00:09:34,770
Got time tonight to come home?

175
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:43,630
You're leaving?

176
00:09:44,230 --> 00:09:45,880
I just got Zhuling to sleep.

177
00:09:47,280 --> 00:09:48,470
Then I... I'll...

178
00:09:59,570 --> 00:10:00,320
Shao Yunfei.

179
00:10:03,100 --> 00:10:03,670
You and Bai Ju

180
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,600
have been divorced for many years.

181
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:07,490
Even though you're Zhuling's father,

182
00:10:07,490 --> 00:10:09,420
we are two families now, after all.

183
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:10,160
Our family doesn't do this

184
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:12,250
"divorced but still hanging around" thing.

185
00:10:12,250 --> 00:10:12,790
Chun,

186
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:14,600
I...

187
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:16,650
I'll always treat you

188
00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:17,680
as family.

189
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,800
That will never change.

190
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:20,530
Shao Yunfei,

191
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:22,630
I'm going to be blunt today.

192
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:23,750
We all know

193
00:10:23,790 --> 00:10:25,770
you still want to
get back together with Ju.

194
00:10:25,770 --> 00:10:26,930
But ask yourself honestly,

195
00:10:26,930 --> 00:10:28,010
have you ever really been a good husband

196
00:10:28,010 --> 00:10:28,940
or a good father?

197
00:10:29,580 --> 00:10:29,980
Chun,

198
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:30,930
this time, I...

199
00:10:30,930 --> 00:10:32,590
We're not that close anymore.

200
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,120
When you two first started dating,

201
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,020
I asked you

202
00:10:36,250 --> 00:10:37,910
about your plans for the future.

203
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:38,930
You said you didn't dare

204
00:10:38,930 --> 00:10:40,340
to think that far ahead yet.

205
00:10:40,340 --> 00:10:41,120
Yes, yes.

206
00:10:41,540 --> 00:10:42,470
I was young then.

207
00:10:42,490 --> 00:10:42,870
But

208
00:10:43,340 --> 00:10:44,000
I've thought it all through

209
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:44,690
very clearly now.

210
00:10:44,690 --> 00:10:46,220
You don't need to answer me.

211
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:48,040
Because the past few years

212
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:50,610
have already given me the answer.

213
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:54,020
You come from a good background.

214
00:10:54,020 --> 00:10:56,750
It's still considered good
by today's standards.

215
00:10:56,750 --> 00:10:57,940
You're from an educated family

216
00:10:57,940 --> 00:10:59,160
and have a job in the provincial capital.

217
00:10:59,160 --> 00:11:00,510
If it weren't for the Mountain Patrol,

218
00:11:00,510 --> 00:11:01,740
you, Bai Ju, and our family

219
00:11:01,740 --> 00:11:02,700
would've been from two different worlds.

220
00:11:02,700 --> 00:11:03,410
We wouldn't have

221
00:11:03,410 --> 00:11:04,270
crossed paths.

222
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:05,790
Our family really
reached above our station.

223
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:07,020
Chun, you... no...

224
00:11:07,390 --> 00:11:08,410
Bai Chun, don't say that.

225
00:11:08,410 --> 00:11:10,670
But our family doesn't owe you anything.

226
00:11:10,930 --> 00:11:13,200
Bai Ju has her hang-ups,
and she can be stubborn.

227
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,150
But when you met her,

228
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,610
she was already like that.

229
00:11:16,530 --> 00:11:17,460
All these years,

230
00:11:17,770 --> 00:11:18,960
she's been raising the kid by herself,

231
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:19,550
while you've been running

232
00:11:19,550 --> 00:11:21,320
all over the country chasing news stories.

233
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,640
When Zhuling had a fever,

234
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:23,100
she was so worried

235
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:24,250
she called me in the middle of the night.

236
00:11:24,250 --> 00:11:25,860
I rushed back from the mine overnight

237
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:26,290
and stayed at the hospital

238
00:11:26,290 --> 00:11:27,530
all night with them.

239
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,320
Every time

240
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:29,740
they

241
00:11:29,770 --> 00:11:31,010
needed you the most,

242
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:32,090
you weren't there.

243
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:34,010
Yes.

244
00:11:35,650 --> 00:11:36,450
That's why...

245
00:11:37,980 --> 00:11:38,890
I want to do my best

246
00:11:38,890 --> 00:11:40,220
to make it up to them now.

247
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:42,510
I'll devote all my time

248
00:11:42,530 --> 00:11:43,530
to making it up to them.

249
00:11:43,530 --> 00:11:44,990
You are Zhuling's father.

250
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,290
Anything you do to make it up to her

251
00:11:46,290 --> 00:11:47,360
could never be too much.

252
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,500
But as for Bai Ju,

253
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:50,100
I advise you

254
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:52,100
to give up on getting back together.

255
00:11:52,890 --> 00:11:53,890
As the eldest brother of the Bai family,

256
00:11:53,890 --> 00:11:55,290
I won't accept you again.

257
00:12:00,450 --> 00:12:01,050
Bai Chun,

258
00:12:02,270 --> 00:12:04,130
you might have misunderstood me.

259
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,170
I love Bai Ju deeply.

260
00:12:06,170 --> 00:12:07,020
I always have.

261
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:09,090
The divorce back then

262
00:12:09,090 --> 00:12:09,990
wasn't my idea.

263
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:11,020
You don't need to explain to me.

264
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:11,960
Yeah, when a man explains too much,

265
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:12,820
it's pathetic.

266
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:14,090
But I think in a relationship,

267
00:12:14,090 --> 00:12:14,650
feeling indebted to each other

268
00:12:14,650 --> 00:12:16,050
isn't really a bad thing.

269
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:17,770
As long as both partners are willing,

270
00:12:17,770 --> 00:12:18,240
others

271
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:19,150
actually don't have the right

272
00:12:19,150 --> 00:12:20,610
to judge or point fingers.

273
00:12:22,310 --> 00:12:23,190
What do you mean by that?

274
00:12:23,190 --> 00:12:24,460
You know what I mean.

275
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,250
Dad.

276
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:40,120
You promised

277
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,980
you'd ride the drop tower with me!

278
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:43,770
Your mom will ride with you.

279
00:12:44,650 --> 00:12:45,860
How can you go back on your word?

280
00:12:45,860 --> 00:12:47,150
We had a deal!

281
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:49,270
The deal was
that your mom would ride with you.

282
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:50,220
You'll ride with me.

283
00:12:50,220 --> 00:12:51,020
Your mom will.

284
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:51,800
You!

285
00:12:51,830 --> 00:12:52,690
Your mother...

286
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:54,360
Hey, language.

287
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,020
How old

288
00:12:56,050 --> 00:12:57,130
are you two?

289
00:13:00,450 --> 00:13:01,670
Boring adult.

290
00:13:01,780 --> 00:13:03,260
Let's ignore her.

291
00:13:03,790 --> 00:13:04,290
Watch out.

292
00:13:04,290 --> 00:13:04,890
Here we go.

293
00:13:09,180 --> 00:13:10,260
You even prepared disposable slippers?

294
00:13:10,260 --> 00:13:10,660
Hello?

295
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,090
I even prepared fruit

296
00:13:13,090 --> 00:13:13,800
and forks.

297
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,570
There's a blanket in the back too.

298
00:13:15,570 --> 00:13:16,090
Dad,

299
00:13:16,250 --> 00:13:17,180
you're the best.

300
00:13:17,870 --> 00:13:18,860
It's just

301
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:21,010
that I don't really like these fruits.

302
00:13:22,160 --> 00:13:23,490
Can I ask you for a favor?

303
00:13:25,170 --> 00:13:26,770
How about you sit in the back?

304
00:13:27,740 --> 00:13:28,600
You see,

305
00:13:28,790 --> 00:13:30,280
big shots and such

306
00:13:30,710 --> 00:13:31,900
all sit in the back.

307
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:32,820
Only secretaries and assistants

308
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:34,220
take the passenger seat.

309
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:35,150
Dad,

310
00:13:35,690 --> 00:13:36,320
these fruits

311
00:13:36,320 --> 00:13:38,080
weren't actually for me, were they?

312
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,340
Of course they were.

313
00:13:39,370 --> 00:13:41,220
Look at the bag of snacks in the back.

314
00:13:41,220 --> 00:13:42,420
Those are all for you.

315
00:13:43,290 --> 00:13:43,870
Okay?

316
00:13:44,460 --> 00:13:46,800
I'll reluctantly

317
00:13:46,870 --> 00:13:47,790
play along with you.

318
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:48,970
You're so good. Come here.

319
00:13:48,970 --> 00:13:51,080
Please get in the car, baby.

320
00:13:51,220 --> 00:13:51,880
Sit tight.

321
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:53,110
I'm closing the door.

322
00:13:54,950 --> 00:13:56,190
All set. We can go now.

323
00:14:08,710 --> 00:14:09,510
What's wrong?

324
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,410
Han found a body.

325
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,380
We...

326
00:14:18,290 --> 00:14:19,950
might have found the Captain.

327
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:26,510
I found the body!

328
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:27,410
Why won't you let us in?

329
00:14:27,410 --> 00:14:28,570
We're processing the scene.

330
00:14:28,570 --> 00:14:29,890
Please cooperate with us!

331
00:14:29,890 --> 00:14:30,570
We're cooperating!

332
00:14:30,570 --> 00:14:31,740
Just let us go in and take a look!

333
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:32,030
Yeah!

334
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:32,790
We're familiar with
the situation back then!

335
00:14:32,790 --> 00:14:33,220
We can help!

336
00:14:33,220 --> 00:14:33,530
I said,

337
00:14:33,530 --> 00:14:34,460
the crime scene is under investigation!

338
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:35,120
Please cooperate with us

339
00:14:35,120 --> 00:14:35,920
and step back!

340
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:40,200
Bai, you're finally here.

341
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:40,600
Bai.

342
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:41,890
Tell them to let us in!

343
00:14:41,890 --> 00:14:42,630
Yeah, Bai.

344
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:43,630
Wait outside.

345
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:44,430
I found the body.

346
00:14:44,430 --> 00:14:45,410
Let us in.

347
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:46,370
Bai.

348
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:47,100
Step back!

349
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,480
Bai!

350
00:14:47,510 --> 00:14:48,680
Step back, all of you!

351
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:49,250
Captain Bai,

352
00:14:49,250 --> 00:14:49,940
the Chief is out of town

353
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:50,460
but is rushing back.

354
00:14:50,460 --> 00:14:51,250
He asked us to have you come

355
00:14:51,250 --> 00:14:51,860
and assist with the investigation

356
00:14:51,860 --> 00:14:53,460
as someone who was involved.

357
00:15:29,430 --> 00:15:30,160
You're here.

358
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:36,700
How is it?

359
00:18:31,030 --> 00:18:32,090
Zhuling is asleep?

360
00:18:32,840 --> 00:18:33,460
Yeah.

361
00:18:34,350 --> 00:18:36,020
She didn't fuss. She was good.

362
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:38,770
Thanks.

363
00:18:52,180 --> 00:18:52,750
Bai Ju.

364
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:58,040
We found him.

365
00:19:12,970 --> 00:19:13,770
That knife...

366
00:19:15,560 --> 00:19:17,400
He showed it off to us.

367
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:24,590
I recognized it immediately.

368
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:29,530
It's still Dolma's.

369
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:31,500
Tashi had someone make
a new sheath

370
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:32,960
with a leather strap for it

371
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:34,580
and insisted on giving it to me.

372
00:19:34,580 --> 00:19:35,580
This is nice.

373
00:19:35,660 --> 00:19:38,120
You should've given me something
like this.

374
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:39,050
What do the words carved on it

375
00:19:39,050 --> 00:19:39,790
mean?

376
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,560
"Gang-ri bzhin."

377
00:19:43,040 --> 00:19:45,440
"As steadfast as a snow-capped mountain."

378
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:01,940
We've reached some

379
00:20:01,940 --> 00:20:03,090
preliminary conclusions.

380
00:20:03,090 --> 00:20:04,310
The deceased is male.

381
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:06,180
Based on the morphological features

382
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:07,250
of the pubic symphysis

383
00:20:07,250 --> 00:20:08,720
and cranial suture closure,

384
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:09,700
we estimate

385
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:13,500
[Tianduo Municipal Public Security Bureau]

386
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,380
the age of the deceased

387
00:20:11,380 --> 00:20:12,440
to be approximately

388
00:20:12,440 --> 00:20:13,750
between 40 and 45 years old.

389
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:14,590
The deceased measured

390
00:20:14,590 --> 00:20:16,660
approximately 1.85 meters in height.

391
00:20:16,660 --> 00:20:17,980
Due to individual variations,

392
00:20:17,980 --> 00:20:18,640
there may be a small margin

393
00:20:18,640 --> 00:20:20,410
of error in the height measurement.

394
00:20:20,410 --> 00:20:21,770
On the left frontal side of the skull,

395
00:20:21,770 --> 00:20:22,680
there is a typical

396
00:20:22,680 --> 00:20:23,810
firearm wound.

397
00:20:24,290 --> 00:20:25,970
The bullet entry hole is circular

398
00:20:25,970 --> 00:20:27,160
with clean edges

399
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:29,780
[Shi Long, Chief of the Tianduo
Municipal Public Security Bureau]

400
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:29,240
and no obvious signs of tearing,

401
00:20:29,270 --> 00:20:30,200
accompanied by minor bone defects

402
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,090
around it.

403
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,330
[Xia Jie, Director of
the Institute of Forensic Science,]

404
00:20:31,830 --> 00:20:33,030
We can basically confirm

405
00:20:32,330 --> 00:20:33,630
[Tianduo Municipal Public Security Bureau]

406
00:20:33,140 --> 00:20:35,160
that the cause of death
was a gunshot wound.

407
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:36,770
Is there an estimate of the time of death?

408
00:20:36,770 --> 00:20:38,190
About 15 years ago.

409
00:20:38,980 --> 00:20:40,380
Trace elements from the soil

410
00:20:40,380 --> 00:20:42,260
have already seeped into the bones.

411
00:20:42,260 --> 00:20:44,090
By analyzing these elements,

412
00:20:44,210 --> 00:20:46,260
combined with the overall weathering
of the bones,

413
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:47,980
we can infer a timeframe.

414
00:20:48,140 --> 00:20:48,750
However, in dry

415
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:49,840
and cold environments,

416
00:20:49,840 --> 00:20:51,250
bone changes occur more slowly,

417
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:52,250
so the estimated time of death

418
00:20:52,250 --> 00:20:54,450
may appear shorter than it actually is.

419
00:20:54,580 --> 00:20:56,640
What's the possible margin of error?

420
00:20:56,830 --> 00:20:57,890
Two to three years.

421
00:20:58,640 --> 00:20:59,240
In other words,

422
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:00,590
the time of death could be

423
00:21:00,590 --> 00:21:02,380
15 to 18 years ago.

424
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:02,950
Yes.

425
00:21:03,530 --> 00:21:04,000
Okay.

426
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:06,500
Doesn't that

427
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:06,770
[Xie Yang, Captain of
the Criminal Investigation Detachment,]

428
00:21:06,650 --> 00:21:07,440
line up with Duojie's disappearance

429
00:21:06,770 --> 00:21:07,950
[Tianduo Municipal Public Security Bureau]

430
00:21:07,470 --> 00:21:08,130
perfectly?

431
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:17,090
What about the forensic analysis?

432
00:21:17,090 --> 00:21:18,440
Most of the clothing on the remains

433
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,660
has decomposed.

434
00:21:19,810 --> 00:21:21,000
At the scene, we recovered

435
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:21,530
a bullet,

436
00:21:21,530 --> 00:21:22,770
caliber 7.62 mm.

437
00:21:23,310 --> 00:21:24,180
The lab is currently

438
00:21:24,180 --> 00:21:25,740
testing other physical evidence

439
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:26,780
that was retrieved.

440
00:21:26,780 --> 00:21:27,320
Okay.

441
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:31,350
Everyone, as you all know,

442
00:21:31,350 --> 00:21:32,680
these skeletal remains

443
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:33,980
are related to

444
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:35,430
a missing person case

445
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:36,460
from 17 years ago.

446
00:21:37,270 --> 00:21:38,660
Our top priority right now

447
00:21:38,660 --> 00:21:39,640
is to confirm

448
00:21:39,810 --> 00:21:41,090
the identity of the body.

449
00:21:41,090 --> 00:21:42,880
Get the DNA extraction done immediately.

450
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,560
Also,

451
00:21:44,090 --> 00:21:45,030
run DNA comparisons against the database

452
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:46,920
for missing persons

453
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:48,500
and fugitives

454
00:21:48,590 --> 00:21:50,380
at the same time.

455
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:51,160
Don't limit

456
00:21:51,250 --> 00:21:52,180
the investigation

457
00:21:52,180 --> 00:21:53,250
to just this one case.

458
00:21:53,250 --> 00:21:53,980
Understood.

459
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:54,640
Everyone,

460
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,380
given the special nature

461
00:21:56,380 --> 00:21:57,240
of this case,

462
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,670
the Municipal Bureau has decided

463
00:21:58,670 --> 00:22:00,270
to form a special task force.

464
00:22:00,510 --> 00:22:02,130
We will mobilize the entire bureau

465
00:22:02,130 --> 00:22:03,990
to thoroughly investigate this!

466
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,590
Xie Yang, after the meeting,

467
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:07,920
come to my office.

468
00:22:08,530 --> 00:22:09,060
Submit

469
00:22:09,090 --> 00:22:10,460
a personnel list for the task force

470
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:12,160
and assign tasks as soon as possible.

471
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:12,690
Yes, sir.

472
00:22:15,460 --> 00:22:16,070
Chief.

473
00:22:18,310 --> 00:22:20,110
I request to join the task force.

474
00:22:20,170 --> 00:22:21,630
Don't even think about it.

475
00:22:22,230 --> 00:22:23,840
You're with the Public Security Brigade.

476
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:24,680
Meddling in such a high-level

477
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:25,200
criminal case—

478
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:26,400
does that make sense?

479
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:27,380
I was personally involved in

480
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:28,780
what happened back then.

481
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:29,790
I have both the qualifications

482
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:30,790
and the responsibility to assist.

483
00:22:30,790 --> 00:22:31,380
Chief.

484
00:22:32,470 --> 00:22:33,190
Besides,

485
00:22:33,220 --> 00:22:34,510
our brigade reported this case.

486
00:22:34,510 --> 00:22:35,640
Han Xuechao has been investigating it

487
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:36,590
for 17 years.

488
00:22:36,890 --> 00:22:38,620
I owe everyone an explanation.

489
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,240
I understand

490
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:40,240
how you feel.

491
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:42,330
Duojie was my former superior too.

492
00:22:42,330 --> 00:22:43,640
But according to recusal regulations,

493
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,200
you cannot participate

494
00:22:44,200 --> 00:22:45,130
in this case.

495
00:22:45,250 --> 00:22:46,380
Don't you know that?

496
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,000
Recuse from what?

497
00:22:49,110 --> 00:22:49,790
The identity of the remains

498
00:22:49,790 --> 00:22:51,140
hasn't even been confirmed yet.

499
00:22:51,140 --> 00:22:52,990
Who am I supposed to recuse myself from?

500
00:22:52,990 --> 00:22:53,610
Don't

501
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:54,640
split hairs here.

502
00:22:55,340 --> 00:22:56,800
You know the regulations.

503
00:22:57,460 --> 00:22:59,040
Go back and do your job properly.

504
00:22:59,040 --> 00:23:00,300
Our brigade's duties—

505
00:23:00,510 --> 00:23:01,700
cracking down on gambling, prostitution,
and drugs,

506
00:23:01,700 --> 00:23:02,900
covering security for large events,

507
00:23:02,900 --> 00:23:03,960
conducting public venue inspections,

508
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:05,570
and managing canine control.

509
00:23:05,570 --> 00:23:06,810
Captain Xiao can handle all of those

510
00:23:06,810 --> 00:23:07,440
with the team.

511
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,700
They don't need me.

512
00:23:10,510 --> 00:23:12,140
What's with your attitude?

513
00:23:13,000 --> 00:23:13,970
Is this how you

514
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,200
treat your work?

515
00:23:16,900 --> 00:23:17,460
If I had known,

516
00:23:17,460 --> 00:23:18,140
I wouldn't have

517
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:19,530
transferred you to the Municipal Bureau.

518
00:23:19,530 --> 00:23:20,330
I should've left you in the county

519
00:23:20,330 --> 00:23:22,380
managing household registrations.

520
00:23:22,380 --> 00:23:23,370
That's not what I mean.

521
00:23:23,370 --> 00:23:24,110
I mean...

522
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:27,130
compared to those routine duties,

523
00:23:27,220 --> 00:23:28,400
Captain Duojie's case

524
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,730
needs me more right now.

525
00:23:30,730 --> 00:23:31,230
See?

526
00:23:32,980 --> 00:23:34,580
That's exactly the problem.

527
00:23:39,750 --> 00:23:40,920
"Captain Duojie."

528
00:23:43,790 --> 00:23:44,500
Bai,

529
00:23:45,290 --> 00:23:46,450
I trust

530
00:23:46,540 --> 00:23:47,870
your professionalism,

531
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,680
but I'm not sure

532
00:23:50,140 --> 00:23:52,240
how much personal emotion
you'll bring into this case.

533
00:23:52,240 --> 00:23:52,710
When it

534
00:23:52,740 --> 00:23:53,900
comes to this case,

535
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:56,210
you can't be both a police officer

536
00:23:56,270 --> 00:23:57,610
and a member of the Mountain Patrol.

537
00:23:57,610 --> 00:23:58,810
I'm a police officer.

538
00:23:59,390 --> 00:24:01,120
I know that better than anyone.

539
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:02,790
Chief,

540
00:24:03,380 --> 00:24:04,580
please rest assured.

541
00:24:05,700 --> 00:24:06,900
Chief, you...

542
00:24:07,450 --> 00:24:08,910
Wait outside for a moment.

543
00:24:09,280 --> 00:24:09,720
Okay.

544
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,050
Chief.

545
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:17,180
I've waited so many years.

546
00:24:17,180 --> 00:24:19,220
This is the day I've been waiting for.

547
00:24:19,220 --> 00:24:20,200
I recognize that knife.

548
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,200
I was involved.

549
00:24:22,000 --> 00:24:22,960
I can definitely help

550
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,400
with the investigation.

551
00:24:25,440 --> 00:24:26,840
Didn't I tell you to wait?

552
00:24:28,790 --> 00:24:29,390
Mayor Lin.

553
00:24:29,800 --> 00:24:30,470
Mayor Lin.

554
00:24:31,090 --> 00:24:31,780
Shi,

555
00:24:32,030 --> 00:24:33,560
I picked someone up for you.

556
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:39,990
Chief Shi Long.

557
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:44,000
You're back.

558
00:24:48,830 --> 00:24:49,460
Ju,

559
00:24:50,700 --> 00:24:51,700
how have you been?

560
00:24:56,860 --> 00:24:57,380
Ju, take a photo

561
00:24:57,380 --> 00:24:58,140
for me.

562
00:24:58,950 --> 00:24:59,450
Okay.

563
00:25:14,790 --> 00:25:15,590
That's right.

564
00:25:17,930 --> 00:25:18,930
This is the knife.

565
00:25:22,770 --> 00:25:24,400
"Gang-ri bzhin."

566
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:28,100
When I carved it,

567
00:25:28,530 --> 00:25:29,120
I thought Dad

568
00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:30,250
was that kind of man.

569
00:25:37,870 --> 00:25:38,640
Actually...

570
00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:41,630
I was prepared for this.

571
00:25:44,030 --> 00:25:45,360
If Dad were still alive,

572
00:25:46,980 --> 00:25:47,850
he wouldn't have abandoned us

573
00:25:47,850 --> 00:25:49,510
and disappeared for 17 years.

574
00:25:53,140 --> 00:25:53,680
Does Cairen

575
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:54,610
know about this?

576
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:57,700
When I came,

577
00:25:58,330 --> 00:25:59,060
I told her

578
00:25:59,090 --> 00:26:03,020
there were some documents
regarding the pasture that needed signing.

579
00:26:04,510 --> 00:26:06,510
Let's wait until the case is closed.

580
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:07,880
After that,

581
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:09,500
I'll find a chance

582
00:26:09,500 --> 00:26:10,900
to break it to her gently.

583
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,540
Actually, since Dad went missing,

584
00:26:14,540 --> 00:26:15,380
Mom's health

585
00:26:15,420 --> 00:26:16,600
has been poor.

586
00:26:18,220 --> 00:26:19,890
It's worrying to have her go to

587
00:26:20,450 --> 00:26:21,650
such a high altitude.

588
00:26:27,080 --> 00:26:28,510
I brought Dad's clothes.

589
00:26:29,540 --> 00:26:30,320
I don't know

590
00:26:30,440 --> 00:26:31,460
if you can still extract

591
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:33,330
the DNA you need.

592
00:26:34,990 --> 00:26:36,440
But we have to try.

593
00:26:38,270 --> 00:26:39,600
Have these been washed?

594
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,640
Spotless.

595
00:26:42,610 --> 00:26:43,740
Mom said back then,

596
00:26:43,990 --> 00:26:45,640
no matter how far Dad went,

597
00:26:45,770 --> 00:26:46,640
the yak dung at home

598
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:47,970
must always be burning,

599
00:26:48,180 --> 00:26:50,040
his clothes must always be clean,

600
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,030
and the butter lamp

601
00:26:51,030 --> 00:26:52,490
must always be lit for him.

602
00:26:53,090 --> 00:26:53,890
Otherwise...

603
00:26:54,530 --> 00:26:56,530
Dad would be angry when he came back.

604
00:26:57,330 --> 00:26:58,610
Can we still contact

605
00:26:59,020 --> 00:27:00,220
his other relatives?

606
00:27:01,950 --> 00:27:02,640
All

607
00:27:03,270 --> 00:27:03,720
his blood relatives

608
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:04,790
have passed away.

609
00:27:06,530 --> 00:27:07,550
I really wish

610
00:27:08,210 --> 00:27:09,810
I were his biological child.

611
00:27:21,220 --> 00:27:21,780
Chief.

612
00:27:23,400 --> 00:27:25,260
Please let me join the task force.

613
00:27:26,110 --> 00:27:27,310
We'll talk about this

614
00:27:27,430 --> 00:27:28,330
later.

615
00:27:28,480 --> 00:27:29,330
Since Mayor Lin,

616
00:27:29,330 --> 00:27:29,760
Captain Xie,

617
00:27:29,760 --> 00:27:31,020
and Tashi are all here,

618
00:27:31,350 --> 00:27:32,530
I promise you—

619
00:27:33,430 --> 00:27:33,830
I won't

620
00:27:33,830 --> 00:27:36,290
let my personal emotions
influence my work.

621
00:27:36,730 --> 00:27:38,290
Before Duojie went missing,

622
00:27:38,290 --> 00:27:39,850
I had the most contact with him,

623
00:27:39,850 --> 00:27:40,310
and I'm also familiar with

624
00:27:40,310 --> 00:27:42,240
his social connections back then.

625
00:27:42,330 --> 00:27:43,090
I can provide more assistance

626
00:27:43,090 --> 00:27:44,460
to the investigation.

627
00:27:44,710 --> 00:27:46,310
It'll only benefit the case.

628
00:27:51,010 --> 00:27:52,140
The case is special.

629
00:27:52,310 --> 00:27:53,460
We do need someone

630
00:27:53,490 --> 00:27:55,140
who understands what happened back then

631
00:27:55,140 --> 00:27:56,140
on the task force.

632
00:27:56,590 --> 00:27:57,290
Besides,

633
00:27:57,660 --> 00:27:59,520
a cross-departmental task force

634
00:27:59,720 --> 00:28:00,420
can integrate resources

635
00:28:00,420 --> 00:28:01,400
and expertise

636
00:28:01,530 --> 00:28:02,550
from all sides.

637
00:28:04,140 --> 00:28:05,140
I think it's okay.

638
00:28:06,510 --> 00:28:07,090
Chief.

639
00:28:07,930 --> 00:28:09,380
I agree with Mayor Lin.

640
00:28:09,920 --> 00:28:11,330
Regarding what happened back then,

641
00:28:11,330 --> 00:28:12,000
the task force

642
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:12,640
intends to interview

643
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:13,840
relevant witnesses.

644
00:28:14,630 --> 00:28:15,960
Having Bai Ju on the case

645
00:28:16,610 --> 00:28:17,520
will help.

646
00:28:22,140 --> 00:28:23,420
Don't get emotional.

647
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:26,140
If you violate any rules or discipline,

648
00:28:26,140 --> 00:28:28,050
go straight back to
the Public Security Brigade.

649
00:28:28,050 --> 00:28:28,580
Yes, sir.

650
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:30,510
Chief,

651
00:28:31,070 --> 00:28:32,030
I now request

652
00:28:32,140 --> 00:28:33,350
the transfer

653
00:28:33,460 --> 00:28:34,920
of all relevant case files

654
00:28:35,080 --> 00:28:37,680
from
the Mazhi County Public Security Bureau.

655
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:48,920
Lin!

656
00:28:49,420 --> 00:28:50,140
Look.

657
00:28:50,590 --> 00:28:51,940
Jianshe bought this for me.

658
00:28:51,940 --> 00:28:52,870
It's quite nice.

659
00:28:53,650 --> 00:28:55,510
Just a bit loose around the waist.

660
00:28:56,690 --> 00:28:57,460
That kid...

661
00:28:58,510 --> 00:28:59,780
He doesn't even know

662
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:00,860
his mother's size.

663
00:29:02,820 --> 00:29:04,490
It's good enough.

664
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:05,930
Our Jianshe

665
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:07,570
is thoughtful enough.

666
00:29:09,330 --> 00:29:10,260
The watch he bought you—

667
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:11,790
I haven't seen you wear it once.

668
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:12,660
Can't bear to?

669
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:14,860
The brand's too fancy.

670
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:16,530
That's true.

671
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:18,880
Next time,

672
00:29:19,290 --> 00:29:19,750
let him buy you

673
00:29:19,750 --> 00:29:20,750
a cheaper one.

674
00:29:20,850 --> 00:29:21,570
Then you can wear it out.

675
00:29:21,570 --> 00:29:22,500
If people ask,

676
00:29:22,590 --> 00:29:22,920
just say,

677
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:23,720
"My son bought this for me."

678
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:25,470
Tashi came to Tianduo today.

679
00:29:30,110 --> 00:29:31,460
Duojie's Tashi?

680
00:29:36,940 --> 00:29:37,990
Tashi...

681
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:39,930
must be over 30 by now, right?

682
00:29:39,930 --> 00:29:41,060
Has he changed much?

683
00:29:44,410 --> 00:29:45,240
He's quieter

684
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:47,600
and more steady.

685
00:29:50,420 --> 00:29:51,350
Not like Duojie.

686
00:29:53,280 --> 00:29:54,540
He's more like Cairen.

687
00:29:58,380 --> 00:29:59,070
Invite the kid over

688
00:29:59,070 --> 00:30:00,330
for dinner next time.

689
00:30:00,670 --> 00:30:02,130
Haven't seen him in years.

690
00:30:08,900 --> 00:30:09,760
At least now...

691
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:13,090
we can get the truth about the case.

692
00:30:16,320 --> 00:30:16,850
What?

693
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,510
All these years,

694
00:30:19,610 --> 00:30:21,010
even if you never said it,

695
00:30:22,120 --> 00:30:23,200
I know.

696
00:30:25,460 --> 00:30:26,640
Neither of us believes

697
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:28,960
Duojie would run away
to escape punishment.

698
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:29,760
Now,

699
00:30:29,870 --> 00:30:31,790
at least we can clear his name.

700
00:30:34,290 --> 00:30:35,950
Can he be considered a martyr?

701
00:30:36,940 --> 00:30:37,790
He contributed to

702
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:39,250
the establishment of the reserve.

703
00:30:39,250 --> 00:30:40,400
The police

704
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:41,850
have to

705
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:43,540
find the killer first, right?

706
00:30:43,880 --> 00:30:44,830
The body's identity

707
00:30:44,830 --> 00:30:45,770
hasn't even been confirmed yet.

708
00:30:45,770 --> 00:30:46,250
Can you stop

709
00:30:46,250 --> 00:30:47,830
jumping to conclusions?

710
00:30:49,340 --> 00:30:51,310
How am I jumping to conclusions?

711
00:30:52,140 --> 00:30:54,800
You're using that official tone with me
at home?

712
00:31:03,410 --> 00:31:04,130
Do you know

713
00:31:04,160 --> 00:31:06,050
you reek of cigarettes when you get home?

714
00:31:06,050 --> 00:31:07,770
You quit smoking years ago.

715
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:09,850
These past few days,

716
00:31:09,850 --> 00:31:11,200
you even

717
00:31:11,390 --> 00:31:12,890
sigh in your sleep.

718
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:16,230
Deep down,

719
00:31:16,250 --> 00:31:17,680
you already have the answer.

720
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:18,170
I just

721
00:31:18,200 --> 00:31:19,270
said it out loud.

722
00:31:44,680 --> 00:31:45,280
Chairman,

723
00:31:45,610 --> 00:31:46,740
you wanted to see me?

724
00:31:46,950 --> 00:31:47,450
Sit.

725
00:31:48,090 --> 00:31:49,220
Have some tea first.

726
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:00,860
When it comes to Pu'er,

727
00:32:01,010 --> 00:32:02,270
the older, the better.

728
00:32:02,550 --> 00:32:03,490
I just got this.

729
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:19,250
Over the last few days,

730
00:32:19,250 --> 00:32:20,580
I visited a few pastures

731
00:32:20,740 --> 00:32:22,600
and finalized all the contracts.

732
00:32:22,910 --> 00:32:23,570
I haven't had a chance

733
00:32:23,570 --> 00:32:24,700
to report to you yet.

734
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:27,860
No rush.

735
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:30,590
All these years,

736
00:32:32,330 --> 00:32:33,240
I've always

737
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:35,520
been confident in your work.

738
00:32:38,270 --> 00:32:38,900
Yaohui,

739
00:32:39,660 --> 00:32:41,190
what year did you come back?

740
00:32:43,830 --> 00:32:44,590
1999.

741
00:32:45,510 --> 00:32:46,010
Right.

742
00:32:47,530 --> 00:32:50,130
The second year
after Xinhai was established.

743
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:52,750
Back then,

744
00:32:52,870 --> 00:32:54,310
Xinhai only had one mine.

745
00:32:57,720 --> 00:32:58,650
In 2000,

746
00:32:58,670 --> 00:33:00,130
things picked up speed,

747
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:02,140
and we opened a few more mines.

748
00:33:02,770 --> 00:33:03,440
I remember

749
00:33:03,460 --> 00:33:06,060
you were still in charge of blasting
back then.

750
00:33:06,250 --> 00:33:07,910
You showed a lot of potential.

751
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:08,870
In 2008,

752
00:33:08,900 --> 00:33:11,300
you'd already become deputy mine manager.

753
00:33:12,030 --> 00:33:13,140
In 2008,

754
00:33:13,430 --> 00:33:14,890
how many mines did we have?

755
00:33:16,130 --> 00:33:16,720
Three.

756
00:33:19,610 --> 00:33:20,920
Then later on, the managers

757
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:22,250
of the subsequent mines

758
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:24,420
must all be your apprentices, right?

759
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:25,890
Yes.

760
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:31,810
Come to think of it,

761
00:33:31,960 --> 00:33:33,640
it's been 16 years

762
00:33:34,400 --> 00:33:35,530
since you came back.

763
00:33:36,250 --> 00:33:36,810
All these years,

764
00:33:36,810 --> 00:33:38,270
you've contributed a lot.

765
00:33:38,870 --> 00:33:39,870
You've done well.

766
00:33:41,030 --> 00:33:42,780
Still, I have to thank you, Chairman,

767
00:33:42,780 --> 00:33:44,840
for the promotions and recognition.

768
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:48,560
Promotions and recognition

769
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:50,280
don't just fall from the sky.

770
00:33:51,790 --> 00:33:53,070
What comes later

771
00:33:54,070 --> 00:33:55,670
is built on what came before.

772
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:00,230
You've never let me down,

773
00:34:02,830 --> 00:34:03,460
right?

774
00:34:06,510 --> 00:34:07,740
You're my boss.

775
00:34:08,590 --> 00:34:10,219
I can't betray your trust.

776
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:16,060
Good.

777
00:34:17,570 --> 00:34:18,360
That's good.

778
00:34:19,739 --> 00:34:21,070
Come on, drink your tea.

779
00:35:56,010 --> 00:35:57,010
I've come and gone

780
00:35:58,110 --> 00:35:58,830
on this road

781
00:35:58,860 --> 00:36:00,260
countless times.

782
00:36:03,090 --> 00:36:03,800
I never thought Dad

783
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:05,060
was buried so close by.

784
00:36:06,730 --> 00:36:07,540
Maybe this was

785
00:36:07,570 --> 00:36:08,700
the Captain's wish.

786
00:36:09,590 --> 00:36:10,820
Like a gatekeeper,

787
00:36:11,070 --> 00:36:12,270
watching over Mazhi.

788
00:36:15,180 --> 00:36:16,710
Until we find the killer...

789
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:20,050
this isn't over.

790
00:36:21,380 --> 00:36:23,990
Life and death are
like the snow on the mountains.

791
00:36:23,990 --> 00:36:25,520
Some melt early, some late.

792
00:36:26,900 --> 00:36:27,820
But in the end,

793
00:36:28,070 --> 00:36:30,330
it all melts into streams and flows down.

794
00:36:31,010 --> 00:36:32,170
That is our karma.

795
00:36:32,360 --> 00:36:33,690
What do you mean by that?

796
00:36:35,150 --> 00:36:36,340
The Captain died mysteriously.

797
00:36:36,340 --> 00:36:37,340
Is this his karma?

798
00:36:37,810 --> 00:36:38,500
Han,

799
00:36:39,130 --> 00:36:39,830
don't twist

800
00:36:39,860 --> 00:36:40,800
Zhacuo's words.

801
00:36:41,590 --> 00:36:42,860
Finding the killer

802
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,280
is easier said than done.

803
00:36:45,690 --> 00:36:47,350
But so many years have passed.

804
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,360
In this vast sea of people,

805
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:49,620
where do we even start?

806
00:36:50,690 --> 00:36:51,750
Just finding the body

807
00:36:51,750 --> 00:36:53,080
took more than a decade.

808
00:36:55,880 --> 00:36:57,050
In Bolamula...

809
00:36:59,090 --> 00:37:00,420
the Mountain Patrol never stopped

810
00:37:00,420 --> 00:37:02,220
just because the road was rough.

811
00:37:05,110 --> 00:37:06,040
On the contrary,

812
00:37:07,690 --> 00:37:08,610
we were best at

813
00:37:08,630 --> 00:37:09,800
digging mud,

814
00:37:11,130 --> 00:37:12,280
slamming the gas,

815
00:37:13,770 --> 00:37:15,430
and pushing the car together.

816
00:37:17,270 --> 00:37:18,920
But sometimes,
even after digging for ages,

817
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:20,250
we still couldn't move.

818
00:37:21,420 --> 00:37:23,350
Once, we were stuck for three days.

819
00:37:27,530 --> 00:37:28,230
Yeah.

820
00:37:30,580 --> 00:37:31,630
That time, we used up all the alcohol

821
00:37:31,630 --> 00:37:32,840
rubbing our legs.

822
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:35,190
For the first time, Han cried

823
00:37:35,190 --> 00:37:36,520
without having a drink.

824
00:37:40,030 --> 00:37:41,450
I used to think

825
00:37:42,280 --> 00:37:44,080
the Captain was very arbitrary.

826
00:37:45,550 --> 00:37:46,690
Later, I realized

827
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:49,420
he was fully aware of

828
00:37:49,420 --> 00:37:50,750
his own arbitrariness.

829
00:37:52,190 --> 00:37:53,750
But what he wanted more

830
00:37:55,390 --> 00:37:57,720
was to eliminate difficulties one by one.

831
00:38:03,210 --> 00:38:04,440
We really had

832
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:06,340
so many troubles

833
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:07,450
back then.

834
00:38:10,920 --> 00:38:12,150
But we can't

835
00:38:14,170 --> 00:38:14,960
just leave a stuck truck

836
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:15,900
sitting there.

837
00:38:19,650 --> 00:38:20,850
Then go investigate.

838
00:38:22,250 --> 00:38:22,920
Ju.

839
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:25,990
Please go investigate.

840
00:38:26,900 --> 00:38:28,160
Find the truth for Dad.

841
00:38:53,700 --> 00:38:55,760
When I said it's hard to investigate,

842
00:38:55,980 --> 00:38:56,400
I didn't mean

843
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:58,200
to stop her from investigating.

844
00:38:59,550 --> 00:39:01,260
I support her fully.

845
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:04,610
I just feel for her,

846
00:39:05,570 --> 00:39:06,320
you know?

847
00:39:09,950 --> 00:39:10,550
I'll pass.

848
00:39:13,860 --> 00:39:15,260
So, you got dumped again?

849
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,700
What do you mean by "again"?

850
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:18,510
True.

851
00:39:19,040 --> 00:39:20,410
There is no "again"

852
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:21,030
because you've

853
00:39:21,030 --> 00:39:22,030
never gotten back together
in the first place.

854
00:39:22,030 --> 00:39:23,090
Get lost, get lost.

855
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,280
Sir, your water.

856
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:26,560
It's fine.

857
00:39:27,010 --> 00:39:28,010
Brother-in-law.

858
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:29,570
As long as I

859
00:39:29,650 --> 00:39:31,780
don't have a new brother-in-law,

860
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:33,050
you'll always

861
00:39:33,050 --> 00:39:34,450
be my real brother-in-law.

862
00:39:34,450 --> 00:39:35,120
No way.

863
00:39:35,380 --> 00:39:36,530
Bai Ji, listen...

864
00:39:37,780 --> 00:39:40,050
you've got to keep an eye on
your sister for me.

865
00:39:40,050 --> 00:39:40,900
If anything happens,

866
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:42,360
report to me immediately.

867
00:39:42,670 --> 00:39:44,350
What could happen to her?

868
00:39:44,530 --> 00:39:45,130
Not to mention she's now

869
00:39:45,130 --> 00:39:46,130
on the task force.

870
00:39:46,380 --> 00:39:47,440
Remember before?

871
00:39:47,550 --> 00:39:48,960
Mom forced her to go on blind dates.

872
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:49,630
How did that turn out?

873
00:39:49,630 --> 00:39:51,070
Do I even need to say it?

874
00:39:52,190 --> 00:39:52,590
Right?

875
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:53,440
Yeah, true.

876
00:39:54,820 --> 00:39:55,510
Bai Ji,

877
00:39:55,840 --> 00:39:57,150
answer me honestly.

878
00:39:57,170 --> 00:39:58,370
Do you think that all these years,

879
00:39:58,370 --> 00:39:59,140
I've been

880
00:39:59,170 --> 00:40:00,360
a good husband?

881
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:05,690
Don't ask me.

882
00:40:06,330 --> 00:40:07,390
Ask yourself.

883
00:40:08,330 --> 00:40:09,660
In any relationship,

884
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:11,070
as long as you have

885
00:40:11,420 --> 00:40:12,400
a clear conscience,

886
00:40:12,400 --> 00:40:13,360
that's enough.

887
00:40:13,380 --> 00:40:14,420
What counts as a "good husband"?

888
00:40:14,420 --> 00:40:16,110
It's all just for show.

889
00:40:18,980 --> 00:40:19,610
Bro,

890
00:40:20,650 --> 00:40:22,110
you are absolutely right.

891
00:40:22,340 --> 00:40:22,780
Yeah.

892
00:40:23,030 --> 00:40:25,030
Bai Chun can't compare to you at all!

893
00:40:26,090 --> 00:40:27,230
Not even close!

894
00:40:29,460 --> 00:40:30,100
Your store

895
00:40:30,130 --> 00:40:31,390
doesn't have a single customer,

896
00:40:31,390 --> 00:40:32,310
and you're glued to your phone.

897
00:40:32,310 --> 00:40:33,440
What are you even busy with?

898
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:33,960
Stop it, stop it.

899
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:34,880
Come on, drink with me.

900
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,610
It's important business.

901
00:40:35,610 --> 00:40:36,090
Forget it.

902
00:40:36,090 --> 00:40:37,230
I'm not drinking today.

903
00:40:37,230 --> 00:40:38,210
You don't know.

904
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:39,530
The restaurant branch I opened

905
00:40:39,530 --> 00:40:40,570
near the mining area

906
00:40:40,570 --> 00:40:41,570
is doing really well.

907
00:40:41,570 --> 00:40:42,630
It's packed every day.

908
00:40:42,630 --> 00:40:43,990
We can barely keep up with
the ingredients,

909
00:40:43,990 --> 00:40:45,720
so I have to make them prep more.

910
00:40:45,900 --> 00:40:46,780
Aren't those small mines

911
00:40:46,780 --> 00:40:48,610
supposed to be suspended
for rectification?

912
00:40:48,610 --> 00:40:49,500
How could they just stop?

913
00:40:49,500 --> 00:40:50,020
If they stopped just like that,

914
00:40:50,020 --> 00:40:50,690
how would the workers

915
00:40:50,690 --> 00:40:51,670
get by?

916
00:40:52,090 --> 00:40:52,730
Work is still

917
00:40:52,730 --> 00:40:53,860
in full swing there.

918
00:41:04,380 --> 00:41:06,440
Captain Bai, aren't you busy?

919
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:08,710
No, I'm not busy today.

920
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:25,280
Captain Bai,

921
00:41:25,820 --> 00:41:26,360
you've been

922
00:41:26,360 --> 00:41:28,050
staring at me here for half an hour.

923
00:41:28,050 --> 00:41:30,450
You're making it impossible for me
to work.

924
00:41:31,900 --> 00:41:32,730
It's been a whole day.

925
00:41:32,730 --> 00:41:34,390
Are the results still not out?

926
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:36,650
The DNA testing technology

927
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,650
was just introduced to our bureau.

928
00:41:38,650 --> 00:41:40,580
The procedures are quite complex.

929
00:41:40,790 --> 00:41:42,100
Be patient.

930
00:41:43,530 --> 00:41:44,840
How long will it take?

931
00:41:46,010 --> 00:41:47,940
At least another two or three days.

932
00:41:48,820 --> 00:41:49,630
We've already expedited it

933
00:41:49,630 --> 00:41:50,510
for you.

934
00:41:51,210 --> 00:41:52,500
Besides, the clothes were washed,

935
00:41:52,500 --> 00:41:54,030
and it's been so many years,

936
00:41:54,300 --> 00:41:56,500
so extracting DNA from them won't be easy.

937
00:41:56,500 --> 00:41:58,100
I understand, I understand.

938
00:41:58,690 --> 00:41:59,150
Come in.

939
00:41:59,150 --> 00:41:59,950
Director Xia.

940
00:42:00,440 --> 00:42:01,690
Some of the text's been recovered.

941
00:42:01,690 --> 00:42:02,190
I've sent it over.

942
00:42:02,190 --> 00:42:02,900
Please take a look.

943
00:42:02,900 --> 00:42:03,570
I'll check it right away.

944
00:42:03,570 --> 00:42:04,000
Okay.

945
00:42:06,750 --> 00:42:07,750
What text?

946
00:42:10,590 --> 00:42:11,760
I'll show you.

947
00:42:11,780 --> 00:42:12,980
I'll just take a look.

948
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:14,960
It's a scrap of paper

949
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:16,760
we found in the victim's pants pocket.

950
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:17,820
It's been too long,

951
00:42:17,960 --> 00:42:19,420
so it's heavily corroded.

952
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:20,000
The document examination unit

953
00:42:20,000 --> 00:42:21,070
is restoring it.

954
00:42:21,740 --> 00:42:23,550
Zhiyuan Freight.

955
00:42:24,400 --> 00:42:25,240
Zhiyuan...

956
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:26,960
Xia Jie,

957
00:42:27,570 --> 00:42:28,480
what kind of paper is this?

958
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:29,340
Is it a receipt?

959
00:42:30,050 --> 00:42:31,900
The paper is torn into several pieces.

960
00:42:31,900 --> 00:42:33,830
We can't piece together a complete one.

961
00:42:33,830 --> 00:42:34,360
There are two more pieces

962
00:42:34,360 --> 00:42:35,530
soaking in solvent.

963
00:42:35,630 --> 00:42:36,190
We have to finish processing them

964
00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:37,250
before we can tell.

965
00:42:38,420 --> 00:42:38,960
Okay.

966
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:43,730
If there's any update,

967
00:42:43,730 --> 00:42:44,520
let me know.

968
00:42:44,550 --> 00:42:45,460
Okay.

969
00:42:45,840 --> 00:42:46,900
I'll be going then.

970
00:42:50,750 --> 00:42:52,120
She's finally gone.

971
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:03,830
All you do is eat.

972
00:43:03,960 --> 00:43:04,800
We have you on the task force

973
00:43:04,800 --> 00:43:05,850
to investigate the case.

974
00:43:05,850 --> 00:43:06,810
I haven't eaten yet.

975
00:43:06,810 --> 00:43:07,610
One last bite.

976
00:43:07,720 --> 00:43:08,380
Hurry up!

977
00:43:08,460 --> 00:43:09,040
Look through the files!
